NAME

DateTime::Locale::nd - Locale data examples for the North Ndebele (nd) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the North Ndebele locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Sibili, 5 Nhlolanja 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Sihlanu, 22 Mpalakazi 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Mgqibelo, 15 Mpandula -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Nhlolanja 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Mpalakazi 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Mpandula -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Nhlo 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Mpal 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Mpan -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B

Bhm (h:mm B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 B

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 B

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Mgq
